00:11:35.409 --> 00:11:36.019
Prof: Pardon me?
 

00:11:36.019 --> 00:11:37.149
Student:  Bound.
 

00:11:37.149 --> 00:11:37.908
Prof: Bound?
 

00:11:37.908 --> 00:11:40.279
Student:  Yeah bound
what we're looking at?

00:11:40.279 --> 00:11:43.779
